<plot>Psychiatric nurse Toni helps suicide-watch patient Maria to escape from the psychiatric clinic she is kept in. Maria's greatest wish is to experience normal life for one week: take care of a few matters, meet people, visit Paris and then bid farewell to the world. Toni wants to accompany her and commit suicide with Maria on the following Sunday. A stirring, sweeping, tragicomic story that cuts deep.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?507074</url></doc>
